{"tid":2398332,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想問吓點發現自己有抑鬱？","createTime":"2021-02-07T08:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T10:27:12.000Z","uid":132174,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1af6cc43e3f95804232a868c96fa053f6f4faee8","tid":2398332,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"近期先知道 一個個性好樂天嘅朋友 幾年前曾經有抑鬱 所以停咗一年學<br />\n嗰期大家都有聯絡 佢停學嗰時大家都有見面 但係我真係一啲都睇唔出<br />\n<br />\n一嚟自己好難確認自己係咪有抑鬱<br />\n二嚟又要害怕身邊嘅人話自己少少事就喺度叫春<br />\n究竟點樣先分辨到普通唔開心同抑鬱？"},{"pid":"d50ac39a87bb2b66604b204ed7e8453283111518","tid":2398332,"uid":95421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},{"pid":"fcc31b3956b50fdd8a03e8aa92a45d485aa022a2","tid":2398332,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d50ac39a87bb2b66604b204ed7e8453283111518","tid":2398332,"uid":95421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"多謝你支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fc4a5d34fc22647b27ac476b88dcd53fbac391","tid":2398332,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"如果唔介意 其實係想聽吓大家發現自己有抑鬱嘅過程<br />\n想多啲留意吓身邊嘅人"},{"pid":"89d6f4590a7c11ff159a2f186a95354581112760","tid":2398332,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"N年前開始，每晚放工即入房，都買半打啤酒，餸酒小食+碗麵，年中無休<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e85158e8ee854aac9d0067113ec4afd52e99ccd","tid":2398332,"uid":386893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1af6cc43e3f95804232a868c96fa053f6f4faee8","tid":2398332,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"近期先知道 一個個性好樂天嘅朋友 幾年前曾經有抑鬱 所以停咗一年學<br />\n嗰期大家都有聯絡 佢停學嗰時大家都有見面 但係我真係一啲都睇唔出<br />\n<br />\n一嚟自己好難確認自己係咪有抑鬱<br />\n二嚟又要害怕身邊嘅人話自己少少事就喺度叫春<br />\n究竟點樣先分辨到普通唔開心同抑鬱？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"我諗主要抑鬱係長時間都因為一件事或一連串事唔開心<br />\n同埋影響到自己身邊其他野<br />\n例如好似你朋友咁<br />\n影響到唔想返學咁<br />\n樓主你自己都有擔心自己咁？"},{"pid":"d363bf84d41290e44a6ac151c8f8e97010c481da","tid":2398332,"uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"Panic attack後大哭 先意識到自己好大問題<br />\n要時間慢慢搵返自己同知自己想點"},{"pid":"e89cd9c8852837dadf818a08a770e57ad0771c70","tid":2398332,"uid":243175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"連飛機都唔想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85d25cc590c46b679e4ee733325e4d3006bed59","tid":2398332,"uid":235729,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:18:30.000Z","msg":"發現自己開始控制唔到情緒，係公眾地方因為好小嘅事，又或者只要係獨處嘅時候都會不自覺地喊。<br />\n每次行到高處望落街都會幻想自己跳落去會點。<br />\n當時聽到一個舊同學因為抑鬱而自殺嘅消息，第一反應唔係傷心而係好羨慕佢可以離開呢個世界。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望你有handle唔到嘅情緒可以搵到信任嘅人同你分擔。"},{"pid":"c53d1aeaf447a54d1341a343da07191fde3ddd29","tid":2398332,"uid":205776,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:24:20.000Z","msg":"完全諗唔到開心嘅事<br />\n我乜都唔想做<br />\n平時自己鍾意做嘅事都冇興趣<br />\n想死 但自己連死哪勇氣都冇 好廢<br />\n做野集中唔到 每日行屍走肉 行路唔帶眼俾車撞<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況小心啲 基本上好少朋友接受到抑鬱嘅朋友"},{"pid":"cae2c540b7ef37c7e752ac63f7d398e57f4c2592","tid":2398332,"uid":368048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8a6ec1b55b0caa070e0256138ecafbf1b421f6","tid":2398332,"uid":238769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"好小事會喊得好西利，唔知仲乜控制唔到情緒，明明以前唔係咁，但父母會話係我自己造成，情緒病係因為自己跳唔出去"},{"pid":"6462812475b2af1b8aa904594e859d89bd3ede57","tid":2398332,"uid":42578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:58:00.000Z","msg":"不停喊，完全唔知自己想點，做人冇晒樂趣，之前有嘅與趣都冇晒，日日都諗住點解父母要生我出嚟，唔知生存嚟做乜，想永遠屈係屋企唔見任何人"},{"pid":"5ad7090e8e394bd104cb1c07501f04b60e60e4a8","tid":2398332,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:01:02.000Z","msg":"你無事嘛朗哥"},{"pid":"9a82da93d3cc21622f0936a66ee1388a47f1028c","tid":2398332,"uid":320204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:01:36.000Z","msg":"瞓醒做嘅第一件事就係瞓回籠覺<br />\n因為發夢開心過喺現實<br />\n瞓到真係攰起身就已經覺得好悶<br />\n於是睇av打飛機/睇連登youtube殺時間<br />\n睇完都得唔到啲咩仲係咁悶諗住去打下機先<br />\n諗到有可能打成幾個鐘結果都係連輸幾場<br />\n於是回復本色<br />\n轉眼間又到應該瞓覺嘅時候<br />\n合埋眼瞓唔著 開始諗下以前同朋友勁開心嘅日子<br />\n諗諗下就覺得點解朋友過得唔錯自己就咁廢<br />\n覺得自己一事無成豪無貢獻對比朋友一個優點都冇<br />\n發覺自己死咗其實對其他人冇影響<br />\n希望自己可以夢中猝死<br />\n重復"},{"pid":"a5c1344fbec4859afb55960012fef796c1205127","tid":2398332,"uid":26699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afedf4e9a95903ee11a81f55e44d0668d201a8a2","tid":2398332,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c1344fbec4859afb55960012fef796c1205127","tid":2398332,"uid":26699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2097822e8e9f2d94f2ccc1717bbead6c4ebb58f7","tid":2398332,"uid":26699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afedf4e9a95903ee11a81f55e44d0668d201a8a2","tid":2398332,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c1344fbec4859afb55960012fef796c1205127","tid":2398332,"uid":26699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc564204838b1e5e7566f151ee5c7be0c414c79","tid":2398332,"uid":2292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c1344fbec4859afb55960012fef796c1205127","tid":2398332,"uid":26699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}